    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ornamental braid or lacing of various patterns in gold and silver, used to trim coats, particularly elements of uniforms. For similar trimming material with scalloped edges, use "galloon."</Note_Text>
